1. Replaced all `x-button` with `x-flux::button`
2. Added proper Flux button attributes:
   - `icon` - using Heroicons names
   - `label` - for button text
   - `size` - consistent sizing (sm/md)
   - `color` - semantic colors (primary/secondary/success/danger/info)
   - `outlined` - for secondary actions
3. Added icons to actions for better visual hierarchy
4. Maintained consistent button sizes throughout the interface
5. Added proper color semantics:
   - Primary actions: solid primary
   - Secondary actions: outlined
   - Destructive actions: danger color
   - Success actions: success color
